---
title: Quick Double Indian Chicken Masala Curry with Rapid Rice & Roasted Cashews
description: There’s nothing better than a curry to warm you up. Let the flavours do all the work with masala curry sauce and golden chicken. Stir through a variety of veg and gobble it down with fluffy rice for a dish that’s basically a hug in a bowl.

